{"tid":2072504,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好似比人呃左錢（急 求救","createTime":"2020-06-20T15:55:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T17:38:54.000Z","uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a5c47eabf9387ece9c4597ffdf6d56138b1f8e78","tid":2072504,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T15:55:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://megapx.dcard.tw/v1/images/ac2c72da-0622-4e62-bc62-f1c1d7535eaa/encode/1280.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmegapx.dcard.tw%2Fv1%2Fimages%2Fac2c72da-0622-4e62-bc62-f1c1d7535eaa%2Fencode%2F1280.webp&h=2d01e6c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前上網搵pt見到個pt好似幾好咁<br />\n<br />\n之後諗住睇下咩尼就申請左..<br />\n（我知我好蠢要鬧就鬧啦...<br />\n<br />\n冇幾耐之後就有人聯絡我問我係咪搵pt<br />\n就叫我比啲個人資料佢<br />\n<img src=\"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/bea5db3f-9b54-4eb5-9eba-b1fe1461de1d/full.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmegapx-assets.dcard.tw%2Fimages%2Fbea5db3f-9b54-4eb5-9eba-b1fe1461de1d%2Ffull.webp&h=897b958a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/966bd718-e15c-4b5b-a580-d0dc7e73eace/full.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmegapx-assets.dcard.tw%2Fimages%2F966bd718-e15c-4b5b-a580-d0dc7e73eace%2Ffull.webp&h=5443f9e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我全部比晒...<br />\n<br />\n份工係幫佢公司做融資...佢話佢同唔同既公司、銀行有合作..<br />\n<br />\n之後叫我去UA、邦民借錢<br />\n因為佢話有合作 做完就會del晒我既資料...<br />\n我信左...<br />\n加加埋埋借左65000..<br />\n之後啲錢入左我戶口<br />\n佢叫我將啲錢比佢個同事<br />\n拎返去會計部計返條數...<br />\n我又比左...<br />\n<br />\n之後今日ua有人打比我<br />\n問我係咪有人叫我借錢<br />\n佢話最近有人報警<br />\n話有人叫學生幫手借錢<br />\n之後比啲錢佢地<br />\n呃學生<br />\n之後個情況同我一模一樣....<br />\n叫我做定心理準備係比人呃晒啲錢<br />\n可能要報警處理<br />\n.............<br />\n<br />\n之後依加好驚...報左警既話會點...<br />\n有冇人可以話我知...."},{"pid":"8fe23c6d7440353a9278ac840ddf0c4f0c3533f9","tid":2072504,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T15:56:00.000Z","msg":"portal: <a href=\"https://www.dcard.tw/f/hkmacdaily/p/233892488\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dcard.tw%2Ff%2Fhkmacdaily%2Fp%2F233892488&d=KvAiISINul4H2q03UsPdud%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=d44074b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dcard.tw/f/hkmacdaily/p/233892488</a>"},{"pid":"324a48c23c3504c521155b8c85004290d5314dca","tid":2072504,"uid":11598,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T15:56:48.000Z","msg":"原來世上真係有啲咁弱智嘅人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔怪得性交轉運真係會work <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27361b40af9288dbc45b5ec21e890ad035e1b0fe","tid":2072504,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T15:58:06.000Z","msg":"做乜轉貼我上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d64e8f2ef2b03b6608847824be92cd9d9f942399","tid":2072504,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T15:58:20.000Z","msg":"俾人呃咗我已經好hurt"},{"pid":"24ab682c23e333c0d913caf915cc8a8432f0a630","tid":2072504,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27361b40af9288dbc45b5ec21e890ad035e1b0fe","tid":2072504,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T15:58:06.000Z","msg":"做乜轉貼我上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T15:58:23.000Z","msg":"比大家笑下都好"},{"pid":"d74d28c9279d79e974a0220c8d1178cb0c085edf","tid":2072504,"uid":74927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T15:58:25.000Z","msg":"戇鳩點救 讀書都咁撚蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28d452905e170a7d45fdb78da333685cac88e6e3","tid":2072504,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid